OL,3,CNotting Hill Carnival fugitive found
OL,4,Cguilty of bus driver's stab murder
OL,6,FA fugitive has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering his ex-girlfriend's father
OL,8,Fafter being caught at Notting Hill
OL,9,FCarnival.
OL,11,FKamar Williams, 34, stabbed Derek
OL,12,FThomas, 55, in Hackney, north-east
OL,13,FLondon, last July 30.
OL,15,FAfter the "frenzied" attack, Williams,
OL,16,Ffrom the Isle of Dogs, east London,
OL,17,Fwent on the run. He was finally
OL,18,Fdetained after crashing a hired BMW
OL,19,Fand fleeing on foot, with police in
OL,20,Fpursuit.
