OL,3,CNotting Hill Carnival fugitive found
OL,4,Cguilty of bus driver's stab murder
OL,6,FOn Monday, a jury at the Old Bailey
OL,7,Ffound Williams unanimously guilty of
OL,8,Fmurder and guilty of having a bladed
OL,9,Farticle by a majority of 11 to one.
OL,11,FThere were cries of "yes" from the
OL,12,Fpublic gallery as the jury delivered
OL,13,Fthe verdicts after deliberating for 17
OL,14,Fhours and 48 minutes.
OL,16,FJudge Angela Rafferty KC adjourned
OL,17,Fsentencing until Friday July 18 and
OL,18,Fremanded Williams into custody.
