OL,4,Cguilty of bus driver's stab murder
OL,6,FAnthony Orchard KC had told jurors the
OL,7,Fdefendant had been looking for the
OL,8,Fvictim's daughter Carron Thomas on the
OL,9,Fnight of the murder.
OL,11,FEarlier that evening, she had received
OL,12,Fthreatening and abusive text messages
OL,13,Ffrom the defendant, the court was told.
OL,15,FThe jury heard that Ms Thomas had
OL,16,Fcalled police twice in the hours
OL,17,Fbefore her father was attacked.
