OL,4,Cguilty of bus driver's stab murder
OL,6,FJust before 7pm, she reported to
OL,7,Fpolice that Williams was at her
OL,8,Fsister's address, but when police
OL,9,Farrived he was not there.
OL,11,FJust after 10.30pm, she called police
OL,12,Fagain, while she was at her sister's
OL,13,Fhouse, believing she could see
OL,14,FWilliams walking through the estate.
OL,16,FWilliams went to Mr Thomas's home
OL,17,Flooking for him or his daughter, but
OL,18,Fthey were not in. As he was driving
OL,19,Faway, he spotted Mr Thomas walking
OL,20,Fhome on Stoke Newington Common at
OL,21,Faround 11pm.
