OL,3,CNotting Hill Carnival fugitive found
OL,4,Cguilty of bus driver's stab murder
OL,6,FMr Thomas had finished a late shift as
OL,7,Fa bus driver and had gone into Tesco
OL,8,Ffor some food before heading home.
OL,10,FWilliams stopped the van he was
OL,11,Fdriving in the middle of the road, got
OL,12,Fout and stabbed Mr Thomas five
OL,13,Ftimes.The contents of Mr Thomas's
OL,14,Fshopping bag were strewn over the
OL,15,Fpavement and road.
OL,17,FMr Orchard said: "Mr Thomas may well
OL,18,Fhave swung a punch at the defendant
OL,19,Fbut if he did, you can be sure he was
OL,20,Facting in a desperate attempt to
OL,21,Fdefend himself.
