OL,4,Cguilty of bus driver's stab murder
OL,6,FFollowing the guilty verdicts,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector John Marriott, of
OL,8,FScotland Yard, said: "This was a
OL,9,Fbrutal and premeditated attack on a
OL,10,Fmuch-loved father.
OL,12,F"Kamar Williams showed clear intent
OL,13,Fthat night, driving to Derek's home,
OL,14,Fwaiting for the right moment, and
OL,15,Fcarrying out this senseless act of
OL,16,Fviolence.
OL,26,@pD@VOUtD@AOU
