OL,6,F"The swift response from our officers,
OL,7,Fcombined with extensive CCTV, forensic
OL,8,Fwork, and determination from our
OL,9,Finvestigation team, led to his arrest
OL,10,Fand conviction.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with Derek's
OL,13,Ffamily, who have shown immense
OL,14,Fstrength throughout this ordeal."
OL,16,FMr Thomas's family said in a
OL,17,Fstatement: "Derek will be greatly
OL,18,Fmissed by his family and friends, he
OL,19,Fwas a dedicated family man and worked
OL,20,Fhard to provide for them. He was the
OL,21,Flife and soul of the family.
