OL,6,F"Derek was always on hand to provide
OL,7,Fsupport, knowledge, advice and was a
OL,8,Fcalming influence when it was
OL,9,Frequired. His passing has left a
OL,10,Fmassive hole in the lives of his wife,
OL,11,Fchildren, grandchildren, family and
OL,12,Fall that knew him. He was greatly
OL,13,Floved by all and will never be
OL,14,Fforgotten."
